Bukola Coker) bụ onye mgbasa ozi na onye nta akụkọ Naijiria
Ọ bụ onye na-akọ akụkọ na Channels TV. Tupu ọ kwaga na Channels TV, ọ bụ onye na-elekọta ihe ngosi TV nke ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị, na TVC News.

Samuel-Wemimo gara St Mary's Private School, Lagos maka agụmakwụkwọ praịmarị ya, gụrụ akwụkwọ sekọndrị na Abeokuta Girls Grammar School, Ogun State na agụmakwụkwọ tertiary ya na Mahadum Lagos State ebe ọ nwetara nzere Bachelor of Arts na History and International Studies.
Samuel-Wemimo malitere ọrụ mgbasa ozi ya dị ka nwa akwụkwọ na Lagos Television na 2001 wee kwaga TVC News na 2006
Na TVC News, ọ rụrụ ọrụ okpukpu abụọ dị ka onye nta akụkọ na onye na-egosi TV, na-akwado Fireworks na Journalist Hangout
N'afọ 2021, Samuel-Wemimo sonyeere Channels TV dị ka onye na-akọ akụkọ. Na Disemba 30, 2020, ndị ọrụ nke Ngalaba Ọrụ Steeti jidere ya.
N'afọ 2017, Samuel-Wemimo meriri City People Awards For Excellence dị ka onye na-egosi TV nke afọ

N'afọ 2019, a họpụtara ya dị ka onye na-eme ihe nkiri telivishọn nke afọ na mbipụta nke iri abụọ na asaa nke Nigeria Media Merit Award mana ọ tụfuru ọnọdụ ahụ n'aka Seun Okinbaloye nke Channels TV. O nwetara onyinye ịja mma maka akụkọ ya gbasara ịda mbà n'obi na igbu onwe ya na 14th Wole Soyinka Award for Investigative Reporting wee gaa n'ihu iji merie ihe nrite Wole Soinka nke iri na ise maka akụkọ nyocha nke Television Category na 2020 maka akụkọ ya banyere mmetọ mmekọahụ na otu ndị uwe ojii si emegbu ụkwụ ikpe ziri ezi. N'afọ 2021, ọ bụ otu n'ime ụmụ nwanyị iri abụọ na otu a họpụtara maka ọzụzụ na ịchọpụta na ịkọ akụkọ gbasara ime ihe ike gbasara mmekọahụ na okike (SGBV) site na The Wole Soyinka Centre for Investigative Journalism (WSCIJ).
